{"id":159716,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/debian下采用pptp连接vpn服务器/","date":"2011-06-10T00:30:26Z","modified":"2011-06-10T00:30:26Z","title":"Debian下采用pptp连接VPN服务器","content":"<p><p>来源：<a href=\"http://hellyguo.wordpress.com/2011/06/05/debian%E4%B8%8B%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8pptp%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5vpn%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/\">http://hellyguo.wordpress.com/2011/06/05/debian%E4%B8%8B%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8pptp%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5vpn%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/</a>    </p>\n<p>一般都在Windows或者iPhone下用VPN，这次拜GFW所赐，maven也无法访问，只能在服务器上临时使用VPN来救急救场。    <br />服务器是Debian，预先装好PPTP。 </p>\n<ol>\n<li>新建VPN连接       <br /><code>sudo pptpsetup --create vpn --server vpnserver --username temp --password temp --encrypt</code> </li>\n<li>连接VPN Server       <br /><code>sudo pon vpn         <br />sudo ip route del default          <br />sudo ip route add default via 192.168.111.1 dev ppp0</code>        <br />如果你还不能上网，譬如我，那就是你的DNS还没有设置对。修改/etc/resolv.conf，新增OpenDNS和Google DNS。        <br /><code>sudo vi /etc/resolv.conf</code>        <br />在最前面新增如下内容： <br />\n<blockquote>\n<p>nameserver 208.67.222.222           <br />nameserver 208.67.220.220            <br />nameserver 208.67.222.220            <br />nameserver 208.67.220.222            <br />nameserver 8.8.8.8            <br />nameserver 8.8.8.4</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>终止VPN连接       <br /><code>sudo poff         <br />sudo ip route add default via 192.168.10.254 dev eth0</code> </li>\n<li>删除VPN连接       <br /><code>sudo pptpsetup --delete vpn</code> </li>\n</ol>\n<p></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/xijie.wordpress.com/4599/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/xijie.wordpress.com/4599/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/xijie.wordpress.com/4599/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/xijie.wordpress.com/4599/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/g